source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_00<tab>Loudjox has run out of wares to sell.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_00<tab>Loudjox fait face à une pénurie de produit.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_01<tab>While Loudjox mistakes you for a customer, she realizes that she can part with some gil in exchange for the leaves of narbroois. Make your way to the Makers' Quarter, and slay the sweetly smelling monsters for six of their fragrant fronds.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_01<tab>Vous avez discuté avec Loudjox, qui voudrait que vous lui rapportiez six <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B1D0302 /var>. Pour ce faire, il vous suffit de vous rendre au quartier des Fabricateurs, dans l'Arrière-pays dravanien, et de vaincre <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0AF20E0D0302 /var>.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_02<tab>You strike down a number of narbroois, and tear the leaves from their still bodies. Find your way back to Loudjox with the aromatic prizes.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez récupéré <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E8B1D0302 /var>. Vous pouvez maintenant retourner auprès de Loudjox, qui vous attend à Idyllée, pour les lui remettre.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_03<tab>Loudjox delivers your payment for the leaves, explaining that they are part of a mixture that goblins place in their masks to avoid bad smells. Given your own experiences with goblin aromas, you decline her offer to take a sniff, and instead take your reward for helping the realm smell just a little better.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_SEQ_03<tab>Vous avez donné à Loudjox ce qu'elle vous avait envoyé<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> chercher. La Gobeline vous a expliqué que ses confrères avaient pour habitude de mettre des plantes aromatiques dans leur masque. Elle avait donc besoin de <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E8B1D0302 /var> pour composer le bouquet garni qu'elle est la seule à commercialiser.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_TODO_00<tab>Collect leaves from narbroois in the Makers' Quarter.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_TODO_00<tab>Récupérer des pousses en terrassant <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0AF20E0D0302 /var> au quartier des Fabricateurs

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the narbrooi leaves to Loudjox.
TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_000<tab>Pssshkoh... Loudjox has <var 1A 02 /var>told<var 1A 01 /var> you, Loudjox has no more smelling herbs for tod─ Hm? Uplander? You have not come with custom?
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_000<tab>Pshhh... Pshhh... Loudjox n'a plus de bouquet garni. Merci de repasser plus tard...<var 1D /var>! Oh, l<var 08 E905 ((a)) ((e)) /var> gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> n'est pas venu<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> en acheter<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_001<tab>Uplander <var 1A 02 /var>wants<var 1A 01 /var> custom? Hmmm... Loudjox <var 1A 02 /var>does<var 1A 01 /var> need six narbrooi leaves for bundle-making of fragrant herbs. From every corpse, uplander can take two leaves─and Loudjox will pay good jinglyshine so we are both happy!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_001<tab>Dans ce cas, Loudjox a un travail à lui confier, car elle ne peut pas abandonner son poste. L'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> serait <var 1A 02 /var>vraiment<var 1A 01 /var> gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> si <var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var> lui rapportait six pousses en tuant <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 02F20E0D0302 /var>. Si Loudjox est contente, l'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> sera encore pluuus content<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_010<tab>Uplander does not know where narbrooi nest? Go to Makers' Quarter─many are floating around there. But make sure monsters are dead first─they are squealing muchly otherwise...
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_010<tab>Pourquoi <var 08 E905 ((elle)) ((il)) /var> n'est pas en train de cogner <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 02F20E0D0302 /var><var 1D /var>? Loudjox a besoin de six <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0D0302 /var><var 1D /var>! Allez, allez<var 1D /var>! Si Loudjox est contente, l'aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> sera encore pluuus content<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_020<tab>Narbrooi make nasty screechings, but their leaves have scent like tastyfresh foods.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_020<tab>L<var 08 E905 ((a)) ((e)) /var> gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> sera très content<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> s<var 08 E905 ((i elle)) (('il)) /var> rapporte six pousses de ces fichus <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF20E0D0302 /var> à Loudjox<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_021<tab>Pssshkoh... Four, five...yes, six full leaves. Thank you uplander. Gobbieflock pack gobbie masks with herbs, keeps nose free of bad smells of bogs and mires. Loudjox can make many bundles, and double jinglyshine!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_021<tab>Pshhh... Pshhh... Loudjox va enfin pouvoir reprendre la fabrication des bouquets garnis<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_022<tab>Would uplander like to smell, too? No? Well, then uplander will want questprize. Loudjox is a gobbie of her word─here is jinglyshine for your service!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ811_01941_LOUDJOX_000_022<tab>Les Gobelins mettent des plantes aromatiques dans leur masque, comme ça, ça sent toujours bon... même quand ça pue<var 1D /var>!
